{"tid":370511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大膽人有錢人船p，淆底獸窮撚勿入。","createTime":"2017-08-23T05:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T06:09:58.000Z","uid":17606,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb874c8c3a3670671d381cd9659f810ed69c35e","tid":370511,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T05:31:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個颱風，我唔係尖咀追風了。等等出海。<br />\n我地book 了3 隻船。第一隻阿爾卑斯山腳式木茷，租的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/132513_b9b9cde904bd2fc757fd05cf03069e7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F132513_b9b9cde904bd2fc757fd05cf03069e7b.jpg&h=d471a5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐30幾人，長10呎。<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的坐20人 亞馬遜式木舟<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/132850_7f4004efb42b086dc34085e1c430b266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F132850_7f4004efb42b086dc34085e1c430b266.jpg&h=da07bc9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我中意呢隻多d，搖少少，寫意d。 <br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通 中式船。 <br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多救生衣。 <br />\n<br />\n星期三 , 3點尖沙咀碼頭集合 <br />\n<br />\n男仔：$1000 位  <br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。 <br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$1000去船河的人吧。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad667298cc453a967e4b1681ae0a28d01151c112","tid":370511,"uid":134864,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"幽默感呢家嘢"},{"pid":"1ec5b959ba8ef45039b1d351950609242ecb08bb","tid":370511,"uid":14130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T05:33:38.000Z","msg":"中式船既圖呢"},{"pid":"09a91e989ffaecdf8de896059a8eb647976fd20f","tid":370511,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中式船既圖呢</blockquote><br